title: Falcon 4.0 - Original ISO
description:
This is a working copy of the original classic flight sim, Falcon 4.0. It is ready to be upgraded with RedViper(Free Falcon) or OF for your enjoyment.

It is compressed with 7-zip, which resulted in a file that is much smaller than a zip. This was done to make it quicker to share this absolute classic for all to enjoy.

7-zip is available here: http://www.7-zip.org/

Please seed this flight sim masterpiece for all to enjoy.
